如果被驱逐，谢菲尔德的 Leadmill 可能会搬到新地点https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-leadmill-in-sheffield-could-move-to-new-location-if-evicted-3823532?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-leadmill-in-谢菲尔德如果被驱逐可以搬到新地点Aneesa AhmedWed, 18 Dec 2024 22:09:45 +0000 Music NewsNewsLive Music NewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3823532 <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="铅磨机。图片来源：Gary Wolstenholme" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>自业主于 2022 年发出驱逐通知以来，该场馆的未来一直充满不确定性</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-leadmill-in-sheffield-could-move-to-new-location-if-evicted-3823532">谢菲尔德的 Leadmill 如果被驱逐可能会搬到新地点的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="铅磨机。图片来源：Gary Wolstenholme" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Leadmill.-Credit-Gary-Wolstenholme-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该公司董事表示，位于谢菲尔德的标志性场所 The Leadmill 如果被驱逐，可能会搬到新地点。</p><p>自 2022 年以来，该场地一直受到威胁，此前该建筑的业主<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-voice-support-for-sheffields-the-leadmill-as-iconic-venue-announces-eviction-and-closure-3195218">发布了驱逐通知</a>，引发了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-voice-support-for-sheffields-the-leadmill-as-iconic-venue-announces-eviction-and-closure-3195218">整个音乐行业和演出观众的强烈抗议</a>。 Leadmill 的法律团队目前正在对该决定提出异议，声称该决定违反了多项法律。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cvgn3yy40n2o?xtor=AL-99999-%5Bpartner%5D-%5BBBC+England%5D-%5Bheadline%5D-%5Bnews%5D-%5Bbizdev%5D-%5Bisapi%5D&amp;at_link_origin=BBCLookNorth&amp;at_medium=social&amp;at_link_id=778175C8-BD47-11EF-9235-F17F3A54A60E&amp;at_link_type=web_link&amp;at_ptr_name=twitter&amp;at_bbc_team=editorial&amp;at_campaign_type=owned&amp;at_format=link&amp;at_campaign=Social_Flow" target="_blank" rel="noopener">英国广播公司</a>报道，</em>该公司唯一董事菲尔米尔斯今天（12月18日）在利兹商业和财产法院举行的驱逐听证会上表示，在该市开设新场地可能是“可能的”。</p><p>米尔斯表示，搬到新地点的可能性是“假设的”和“B 计划或 C 计划”。导演表示，A 计划是“我们在这个案子中取得成功，并继续下去。”</p><p>这座可容纳 900 人的场馆大楼的所有者 Electric Group 于 2022 年 3 月向其租户 The Leadmill Ltd 发出了驱逐通知。Leadmill Ltd 拥有该场馆名称的商标，这意味着位于不同建筑的新场馆可以保留该名称以及原创的品牌。</p><p>然而，米尔斯表示，The Leadmill 的新址可能“不一定”位于谢菲尔德。 “如果我们在谢菲尔德找到合适的场所，我们实际上就是在与自己竞争，因为 The Leadmill 的名字和遗产在我们的客户心目中是不可分割的，”他说。</p><p> “[电气集团老板][多米尼克]马登先生在声明中表示，[场地]将永远被称为 The Leadmill，他说得很对。老特拉福德球场将永远被称为老特拉福德球场。”</p><p>本周早些时候，电气集团老板多米尼克·马登 (Dominic Madden)<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/cy53w2q95gno" target="_blank" rel="noopener">指责</a>他的租户对场馆的翻新成本做出了“荒谬的过度”估计。</p><p>听证会继续进行。</p><p>当地新闻媒体<a href="https://www.thestar.co.uk/news/politics/plan-for-the-partial-demolition-of-sheffields-iconic-the-leadmill-building-submitted-4914758" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《谢菲尔德星报</em></a>》报道称，一项旨在部分拆除 The Leadmill 以改善“该地区的视觉特征”的新计划已<a href="https://www.thestar.co.uk/news/politics/plan-for-the-partial-demolition-of-sheffields-iconic-the-leadmill-building-submitted-4914758" target="_blank" rel="noopener">提交</a>，正在等待批准。谢菲尔德市议会的规划官员必须在 2 月 3 日之前就该提案的结果做出决定。</p><p>自 1980 年开业以来，这个独立场地曾接待过<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队 (Coldplay)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-stone-roses">石玫瑰乐队 (The Stone Roses) 等乐队。</a></p><p> 2022 年，该场馆收到驱逐通知后，前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jeremy-corbyn-joins-campaign-to-save-sheffield-leadmill-3227527">工党领袖杰里米·科尔宾 (Jeremy Corbyn) 参观了 The Leadmill，并鼓励其他人“支持它……”</a> 。</p><p>他还呼应了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/leadmill-sheffield-eviction-closure-arctic-monkeys-tour-manager-local-reaction-3201505">无数谢菲尔德当地人的观点</a>，将其誉为“城市的心脏”，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/local-stars-rally-around-leadmill-as-new-owners-register-for-name-electric-sheffield-3197594">谢菲尔德艺术家中的 Arctic Monkeys、Jarvis Cocker 和 Bring Me The Horizo​​n 的 Oli Sykes 等纷纷发声支持的场地</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-leadmill-in-sheffield-could-move-to-new-location-if-evicted-3823532">谢菲尔德的 Leadmill 如果被驱逐可能会搬到新地点的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
