ading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Cures-Robert-Smith-performing-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Cures-Robert-Smith-performing-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Cures-Robert-Smith-performing-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Cures-Robert-Smith-performing-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Cures-Robert-Smith-performing-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/The-Cures-Robert-Smith-performing-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/The-Cure">The Cure 乐队</a>的<a href="/artists/Robert-Smith">罗伯特·史密斯</a>(Robert Smith) 公开谈论了他在摇滚名人堂的采访，并透露他对此“感觉很糟糕”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-cure-songs-of-a-lost-world-review-lyrics-3801637">治愈——“失落世界之歌”：对失落的巧妙反思</a></strong></li></ul><p>早在 2019 年，史密斯和他的同事们在纽约颁奖典礼上走过红地毯并入选摇滚名人堂时，就接受了这一荣誉、他们漫长的职业生涯以及新音乐的进展。</p><p>在地毯上的第一次聊天中，The Cure 遇到了一位热情的采访者，他也承认自己是 The Cure 的超级粉丝。 “恭喜 The Cure 入选 2019 年摇滚名人堂！你也和我一样兴奋吗？！”她问道。</p><p>史密斯给出了典型的面无表情和直率的回答：“听上去，没有。” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cures-robert-smith-goes-viral-brilliantly-blunt-brand-interview-response-watch-2469439">此后，这段互动的片段在《男孩别哭》制作人的粉丝中疯传，</a>他们称这一时刻“无价”、“美妙的英国风格”和“令人捧腹的欢乐”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="The Cure 的罗伯特·史密斯对过度热心的电视主持人做出了直率的回应" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/houFuiYrEi0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>现在，这位主唱在 BBC Sounds 节目中以嘉宾身份出现在安妮·麦克马纳斯 (Annie MacManus) 和尼克·格里姆肖 (Nick Grimshaw) 的播客<a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/gd/podcast/sidetracked-with-annie-and-nick/id1708242412" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Sidetracked with Annie and Nick</em></a> 》中，讲述了这一时刻。</p><p> “事实上，我对此感到很难过……说实话，我并没有意识到我正在被拍摄。所以，这可能就是为什么……我们刚刚在更衣室里就我们在那里所做的事情进行了一次非常严肃的谈话。这股热情就像……[笑声]。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DDuNxrbovs4/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 5